§ SUBSYSTEMS-CONSUMING-OMEGAFIELD  (downstream contract)

  § STAGE-3 OmegaFieldUpdate-pipeline-stage
    consumes : OmegaField (mutable in async-compute)
    produces : updated FieldCell-grid + overlays + MERA-tier 1..3 summaries
    runs all-6 phase-hooks in canonical order

  § STAGE-4 WaveSolver
    consumes : OmegaField.field-cells (S facet) + Λ-overlay
    produces : ψ-field-band-states (cssl-wave-solver internal)
    feeds : Stage-7 RC GI consumes ψ-substrate via probe_lo/hi (P facet)

  § STAGE-5 SDF-raymarcher (cssl-render-v2)
    consumes : OmegaField.field-cells (M facet for SDF-eval) + Σ-low (occlusion)
    produces : GBuffer + VolumetricAccum
    Σ-mask-aware : skips raymarch through Frozen/Halted cells per consent

  § STAGE-6 KAN-BRDF (cssl-spectral-render)
    consumes : RayHit + KanMaterial-handle (M facet) + light-direction
    produces : 16-band SpectralRadiance (¬ RGB until Stage-10)

  § STAGE-7 Fractal-amplifier (cssl-fractal-amp)
    consumes : Surface-fragments + KAN-weights
    produces : sub-pixel-displaced positions
    Σ-mask-aware : ¬ amplify Frozen-cell surfaces

  § STAGE-8 CompanionSemantic (cssl-render-companion-perspective)
    consumes : OmegaField + companion-context
    produces : companion-perspective semantic-overlay
    Σ-mask-aware : ¬ surveillance-mirror ; consent-protected-rendering

  § STAGE-9 Mise-en-abyme (cssl-render-v2::mise_en_abyme)
    consumes : recursive-witness-cells (Φ-handle = Witness)
    produces : recursive-frame at mirror-hit (no spy-mirror)

  § PHYSICS-WAVE (cssl-physics-wave)
    consumes : OmegaField.field-cells (S + M facets) + ψ-couple
    produces : XPBD-GPU constraint-graph + body-plan-tracking
    Σ-mask-aware : ¬ coerce-cells without Modify consent

  § PROCEDURAL-ANIM (cssl-anim-procedural)
    consumes : KAN-genome + Φ-handle (creature semantic-id)
    produces : pose-from-genome + PGA-Motor joints
    Σ-mask-aware : creature-eye-Sovereign protections

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

§ VALIDATION  (reimpl-from-spec gate)

  § REIMPL-CONTRACTS (impl-must-honor)
    R-1 : FieldCell layout exactly-matches § BYTE-LAYOUT (72B std430)
          new-fields = spec-amendment ; rename = major-version-bump
    R-2 : Morton-key encoding bit-equal-across-hosts (§ DETERMINISM-CONTRACT)
    R-3 : Σ-mask layout exactly-matches § BIT-LAYOUT (16B std430)
          consent-bits-FROZEN ; reordering = ABI-break
    R-4 : EnforcesΣAtCellTouches pass emits SIG0001..SIG0010 verbatim
    R-5 : 6-phase omega_step contract — phase-order matches § THE-6-PHASES
    R-6 : Wave-Unity 5-band default config (§ BAND-CONFIG) is stable-set
    R-7 : LIGHT→MANA + AUDIO→MANA = 0 STRICT-ZERO-ENFORCED at-runtime
    R-8 : Σ-check non-optional ∀ set_cell ; revoking-overrides forbidden
    R-9 : ∀ replay-test produces bit-exact-OmegaField on identical-inputs
    R-10: MERA cascade tier-count = 4 ; coarsening-rate = 8-to-1

  § ORACLE-MODES (§§ 23 applied to Substrate-v2)
    @replay              : 6-phase tick ×N bit-exact (R-9)
    @layout_test         : LAY0001 + 72B + std430 verified-by-runtime
    @sigma_pass_test     : SIG0001..SIG0010 all-emit on canonical violators
    @cross_host_replay   : Morton-key bit-equal Intel ↔ AMD ↔ Apple-Silicon
    @audio_callback      : Phase-2 AUDIO-band honors {Realtime<Crit>, Deadline<1ms>}
    @conservation_test   : ψ-norm preserved per-band ; HEAT absorbs losses
    @consent_revocation  : revoke-mid-step ⇒ effects-skip-this-tick + Audit
    @kill_switch         : ω_halt() observed by-Phase-5 ; tick-completes-cleanly
    @biometric_egress    : Privilege<*> CANNOT authorize biometric ⇒ structural-refuse
    @path_hash_only      : raw-path-strings refuse-egress at telemetry-ring boundary
    @attestation_chain   : audit-chain root = Apocky-Root signed ; Ed25519 verifiable

